  <brief_title>Long-term Study of Safety and Efficacy of Roflumilast in Japanese Patients With Bronchial Asthma (20 to 71 y) (APTA-2217-07)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Long-term Study of APTA-2217 in Adult Patients With Bronchial Asthma</official_title>
